{
  "stem": "14060.9",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I had a ping-pong ball, a racquet, a tefillin, and a salami in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, I looked like a day tripper on a bicycle going out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In case they stopped me, I said, look, I'm going to this-and-this guy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "No problem.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At 9 o'clock in the evening-- this was in April, end of April-- I went-- we went out to his mountainside hut, which was part of this little vineyard.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we waited till it was getting dark.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We started to go through the wires, and even in the stillness of early evening night, the movement of the wire was heard by one of the Hungarian guards.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But he, fortunately, had a very weak torch, and he shouted after us, stop, or I shoot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were practically through the second set of wires.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I left my overcoat, my tefillin, everything there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I ran with this guy, who was navigate-- getting me through, for approximately a kilometer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I will-- don't forget how out of breath I was, because it was frightening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because, don't forget, if I was caught, I was 19 years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I was of military age.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I would have got 5 or 10 years, and I would have never seen daylight after that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Anyway, they didn't come after us, because you see what happened was the Hungarian border guards notified the Russians on the Austrian side, which was also Russian zone, and they started searching for people.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It happened very often.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Anyway.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Danger passed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I was taken to a-- a house of-- of one of these agricultural people there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You know, the [NON-ENGLISH], as you call it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The peasant house, where I was kept till 4:00, 5:00 in the morning when there was an early bus going up to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I got some sort of identity paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
